<b><a href="Disco" title="Disco">Disco</a></b> is within the scope of the <b><a href="Wikipedia_WikiProject_Music/Music_genres_task_force" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Music/Music genres task force">Music genres task force of the Music project</a></b>, a user driven attempt to clean up and standardise <a href="Music_genre" title="Music genre">music genre</a> articles on Wikipedia. Please visit the task force <a href="Wikipedia_WikiProject_Music/Music_genres_task_force/Guidelines" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Music/Music genres task force/Guidelines">guidelines</a> page for ideas on how to structure a genre article and help us <a href="Wikipedia_WikiProject_Music/Music_genres_task_force/Assessment" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Music/Music genres task force/Assessment">assess and improve</a> genre articles to <a href="Wikipedia_What_is_a_good_article" title="Wikipedia:What is a good article" class="mw-redirect">good</a> and <a href="../Wikipedia_Version_1.0_Editorial_Team" title="Wikipedia:Version 1.0 Editorial Team">1.0</a> standards.</td>
